  "title": "fix(hierarchicalMenu): pass correct attribute name to Insights",
  "body": "When clicking on facets in a `hierarchicalMenu`, the passed `attribute` is always the first one passed in the [`attributes`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/hierarchical-menu/js/#widget-param-attributes) option, no matter what level it actually is.\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5370675/193083634-ba433032-135d-4535-abb9-5cf9fbd8a58f.mov\r\n\r\nThis fixes it by inferring the level based on the `facetName` by splitting on `separator`.\r\n\r\nFX-1801",
